<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1908-05-28T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1908-05-28T00:00:00-05:00" n="661" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d661">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 3742/5–A.</note>
                        <head><hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to
                                President-elect <persName type="to">Leguia</persName>.</hi></head>
                        <opener><seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg></opener>
                        <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/><hi rend="italic">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1908-05-28"><hi rend="italic">May 28,
                                1908</hi></date>.</dateline></opener>
                        <p>Mrs. Root joins me in hearty and sincere congratulations upon your
                            election to the Presidency of Peru, and in the best wishes for a
                            successful and glorious administration.</p>
                        <closer><signed><hi rend="smallcaps">Elihu Root.</hi></signed></closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>